password.description:
"User's password (may contain Latin letters, numbers, and symbols;
- signs can be in different cases; 
- can contain from 8 to 64 characters (inclusive);
- cannot contain spaces)"

get.description:
Retrieves a board by its ID and sets it as the active board for the user.
If a `previous_boardId` is provided in the request body, it will be deactivated; 
if not, all boards of the user will be deactivated.
